@*
    Inline status pill for an AuthEventLog row's EventType. Same theme
    as AuditActionBadge but mapped to the authentication-event states.

    SignInSucceeded   → "active"   (positive / current)
    TokenIssued       → "archived" (informational / low-signal)
    SignOut           → "archived" (informational)
    SignInFailed      → "inactive" (warn — credential-stuffing signal)
    LockoutTriggered  → "inactive" (warn — strongest signal in the feed)
*@

<span class="enki-status-pill @PillClass">@EventType</span>

